name: Me myself and I
description: Let’s get to know each other. I’m Dora, who lives in Russia and likes not to like Russia. I smell different perfumes, and I put on my hands a cream that smells like a forest ranger. I have a lot of complexities, but I think all women are perfect. I have a lot of art film dreams and someday I’ll make a film about them. When I meet a man I always look at his shoes and hands. I love the smell in the Moscow subway. I’m terrified of old age and gypsies
